      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and can still be a solid option for someone who needs basic, affordable transport. Great for a project, a spare vehicle, or a handy runaround with some character. Priced to sell and offered by someone who believes in being straight with buyers\u2014come take a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
