    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily-with-character. This car has a strong, substantial road feel and offers a well-sorted platform for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and easy serviceability. Engine starts, runs, and delivers dependable motivation, while the chassis, drivetrain, and suspension components provide a good foundation for continued use or gradual improvement. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. Great opportunity to get into an affordable vehicle with practical utility and plenty of upside for the next owner.",
